name: Soul kadi - Seafood Kitchen and Bar

reviews.review_text:
Food here is heavenly ! We had butter garlic calamari and thali. Just yum !!
Service is great here and not to worry about parking.

Overall good experience in food drinks and cocktails. We just went randomly y looking reviews on map. The food I ordered was Pomfret thali, chicken tikka masala. Cocktail- Soulkadi and whiskey 100 pipers. Everything we ordered was simply great tasty and delicious.  Would recommend highly to visit this place. Simply the atmosphere is great, situated in farm with all authentic vibes. Just what I was searching for!!! Price for drinks and food was budget friendly. We visited Goa for 5 times in a single Year but never found such relaxing place.

After a lot of searching finally found a seafood and goan thali place! Loved the stuffed calamari. We also had mussels rawa fry and king fish thali and for drink we had fresh lime soda. Total it costed us 1975 inr. Will totally recommend coming here.

description:
**Discovering Soul Kadi: A Culinary Gem in Anjuna**

Nestled in the vibrant coastal town of Anjuna, **Soul Kadi - Seafood Kitchen and Bar** has garnered a solid rating of **4.1** from **1166** reviews, positioning it as a must-visit sanctuary for seafood aficionados. This delightful restaurant shines particularly bright with its specialties in **thali**, emphasized by **99 mentions**, along with **Goan** delicacies, **pomfret**, and the refreshing **sol kadhi**.

**Ambiance & Design**

Soul Kadi captivates from the moment you step in, enveloped in an inviting ambiance that blends rustic charm with a tropical twist. The interior showcases traditional Goan décor, complete with soft lighting and earthy tones that create a relaxing atmosphere. Patrons have noted the authentic vibes, enhanced by the restaurant’s location on a lush farm, giving diners a sense of dining amidst nature. The photos reveal cozy nooks and tables adorned with fresh local flowers, adding to the inviting allure of the space.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The highlight of the menu is undoubtedly its **seafood offerings**, with several dishes listed among customer favorites. Reviewers rave about the **butter garlic calamari** and the **variety of thalis**, including the coveted **pomfret thali**. The presentation of dishes, showcased in vibrant photos, displays generous portions artfully arranged—a testament to the chef’s commitment to both taste and visuals. The **stuffed calamari** and **king fish thali** are particularly recommended, reflecting both the freshness of ingredients and the depth of Goan influences in the cooking.

For those seeking a cool refreshment, the **sol kadhi** cocktail has received notable mentions, perfectly balancing its tangy freshness with the richness of coconut. Additionally, the restaurant caters to varied dietary preferences, ensuring something for everyone.

**Customer Experience & Service**

Feedback on customer service has been overwhelmingly positive, with diners highlighting the friendly and efficient staff, making the overall dining experience a pleasure. Comments on the ease of parking and the restaurant’s accommodating policies for walk-ins have further solidified its reputation as a hassle-free dining choice. After all, with delightful food and a tranquil setting, the last thing you want is to worry about logistics.

**Popularity & Reviews**

As evidenced by its impressive rating and the volume of reviews, Soul Kadi has made a significant mark in the culinary scene, especially among both locals and visitors. Many have discovered this gem through online reviews, praising not just the food but the whole experience it offers. Guests have shared their enthusiasm on social media, and the buzz surrounding this establishment only seems to grow with each satisfied patron. 

**Utilizing Visual Content**

Images shared by patrons highlight both the enticing food and the charming décor. The beautifully plated calamari and thali dishes look almost too good to eat, while the vibrant ambiance is captured in the cozy seating arrangements and nature-inspired decor. This visual appeal enhances Soul Kadi’s story, inviting new visitors to revel in the aesthetic pleasure as much as the culinary delights.

**In Conclusion**

Soul Kadi - Seafood Kitchen and Bar continues to thrive as a beloved restaurant in Anjuna, combining fantastic food with a serene environment and warm hospitality. Whether you’re a seafood lover or simply in search of a laid-back dining experience amidst beautiful surroundings, Soul Kadi promises not just a meal, but a delicious memory. Plan your visit and immerse yourself in the flavors of Goa!
